name: mega_loop_while_nested_unless_accumulates_odd_hits
section: codegen-control-loops
args: 
type: Bool
expect: True
description: while with nested unless and modulo must count odd loop indexes.
law: (= (with [i 0 hits 0] (do (while (< i 6) (begin (unless (= (% i 2) 0) (set! hits (+ hits 1))) (set! i (+ i 1)))) hits)) 3)
